reviewText: Purchased for an upcoming field trip, very informative!
An excellent product. Loved Ken Ham's story!  It really makes our family want to take the trip to see the museum.

I bought this DVD because we went through the museum this past June and it was amazing! I wanted something to remember it by. If you can't get up to Kentucky any time soon, this DVD is a VERY detailed walk through of the museum and it's exhibits!
